There are a number of options for getting in contact with responsible
people for %%site.name%%.

Bugs
----

If you think you've found a bug in the Rainbow Dash Network software, or if there's a new feature you'd like to see, 
alert an administrator through either of the options listed below. Note that our software is heavily modified from 
the original distribution of [StatusNet](http://status.net), so bugs encountered here should not be filed with their 
bug tracker.

Email
-----

You can reach the responsible party for this server at [%%site.email%%](mailto:%%site.email%%).

Post a notice
-------------

If you have a question about how to do something, just post a notice
with your question. Watch your inbox or the [public timeline](%%action.top%%)
for answers.

